{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DR59yZXpNBxrgQ6VUmP2Rv","type":"tool_result","content":"440\t\n441\t| Skill | Change |\n442\t|-------|--------|\n443\t| `skills/harness-run/` | Update to reference workflow-engine |\n444\t| `skills/harness-status/` | Update to reference workflow-state |\n445\t| `skills/harness-init/` | Update for new init flow |\n446\t\n447\t#### NEW (20+ files)\n448\t\n449\t- 7 core modules in `src/lib/` (workflow-parser, agent-resolver, workflow-engine, agent-dispatch, evaluator, circuit-breaker, workflow-state)\n450\t- 3 JSON schemas in `src/schemas/`\n451\t- 9 agent YAMLs in `templates/agents/`\n452\t- 1 workflow YAML in `templates/workflows/`\n453\t- 1 new command (`src/commands/validate.ts`)\n454\t- Co-located tests for all new modules\n455\t\n456\t### FR → Module Mapping\n457\t\n458\t| FR Group | Module |\n459\t|----------|--------|\n460\t| FR1-6, FR13-15 (Workflow + Config) | workflow-parser |\n461\t| FR7-12 (Agent Config) | agent-resolver |\n462\t| FR16-18, FR29-31 (Execution + Feedback) | workflow-engine |\n463\t| FR19-23 (Dispatch) | agent-dispatch |\n464\t| FR24-28 (Verification) | evaluator |\n465\t| FR32-35 (Circuit Breaker) | circuit-breaker |\n466\t| FR36-37 (Observability) | agent-dispatch (trace IDs) |\n467\t| FR38-41 (CLI) | commands/*.ts |\n468\t\n469\t### Dependency Chain Breaks to Handle\n470\t\n471\t| Deleted Module | Dependents That Need Cleanup |\n472\t|---------------|------------------------------|\n473\t| `beads.ts` | bmad.ts, epic-generator.ts, onboard-checks.ts, bridge, github-import, init, onboard, retro-import, status, sync, verify |\n474\t| `beads-sync.ts` | sync.ts, verify.ts, run.ts |\n475\t| `verify-parser.ts` | verify.ts |\n476\t| `verifier-session.ts` | (no external dependents — self-contained) |\n477\t| `patch-engine.ts` | bmad.ts, teardown.ts |\n478\t| `retry-state.ts` | retry.ts (deleted), run.ts |\n479\t| `state.ts` | verify.ts, status.ts, state.ts command, init.ts |\n480\t| `ralph-prompt.ts` | run.ts |\n481\t| `showboat-template.ts` | verify.ts |\n482\t\n483\t### Integration Boundaries & Data Flow\n484\t\n485\t```\n486\tcodeharness run\n487\t  → workflow-parser: load + resolve workflow YAML\n488\t  → agent-resolver: resolve all referenced agents, cache\n489\t  → workflow-engine: execute flow steps\n490\t    → per-story tasks:\n491\t        agent-dispatch: SDK query() → agent works → returns\n492\t        workflow-state: write checkpoint\n493\t    → per-run tasks (verify):\n494\t        evaluator: setup workspace → agent-dispatch → parse verdict\n495\t        workflow-state: write checkpoint + scores\n496\t        circuit-breaker: evaluate stagnation\n497\t    → loop block: repeat with findings injected\n498\t  → workflow-state: write final status\n499\t```\n500\t\n501\t## Architecture Validation Results\n502\t\n503\t### Coherence Validation\n504\t\n505\t**Decision Compatibility:** All technology choices (Agent SDK + TypeScript + commander + yaml) are Node.js ecosystem, no conflicts. Agent SDK async generator + sequential engine execution are compatible. JSON schema validation consistent across workflow, agent, and verdict schemas.\n506\t\n507\t**Pattern Consistency:** kebab-case files + camelCase exports matches existing codebase. snake_case YAML keys is standard cross-language convention. Write-after-task state pattern aligns with crash recovery requirement.\n508\t\n509\t**Structure Alignment:** 7 modules in `src/lib/` with co-located tests matches existing structure. Templates in `templates/` matches existing distribution. `.codeharness/` for project config is clean separation from `.claude/`."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Kwq1jWkHGueReqZtY8JQZo","session_id":"0dddd908-79fb-4621-81f1-f9e1a3ee8324","uuid":"8d237805-0c1d-4d95-af81-bb2df867df15","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:56:24.943Z"}
